data.description: **PRICE IMPROVEMENT! SELLER IS WILLING TO OFFER CLOSING OR PARTICIPATE IN A RATE BUYDOWN! Welcome Home! Excellent chance to purchase in Aberdeen's Lyndhurst subdivision. From the ground up, this beautiful home has been completely renovated to meet modern requirements for style, energy, and function. As you approach the home, you'll take notice of the beautiful stone front facade and lovely covered front porch, complimented by the meticulous landscaping. Enter the home to find a spacious, open living area with vaulted ceilings, recessed lighting, a ceiling fan, luxury vinyl flooring, and an abundance of natural lighting. Every possible feature and amenity can be found in this custom kitchen which is open to the large living room. These amenities include 42" white shaker style cabinets, ceramic flooring, granite counters, whirlpool stainless steel appliances, recessed lighting throughout. Convenient side entrance leading to laundry/mudroom with cabinets, ceramic flooring, washer- dryer, and laundry sink. Three large bedrooms including primary bedroom suite with vaulted ceilings, recessed lighting, ceiling fan, custom built in window seat, large walk-in closet. En-suite bath features custom ceramic tile and glass shower doors. Two additional bedrooms with luxury vinyl flooring and ceiling fans. Hall bath features glass shower doors and custom ceramic tile. There was not a single detail overlooked during construction of this home. This includes entire house sprinkler system coax cable and usb outlets throughout, double hung vinyl windows, vinyl siding, soffit, fascia, gutters and downspouts. Only top-quality materials were used during construction of this home including GAF architectural shingles and Trane high efficiency natural gas heat and central air conditioning. The outside of the home features a  6’ vinyl privacy fence in the rear yard, sidewalk leading to stamped concrete patio with pergola and outdoor tv, large custom-built shed equipped with electric great for storage or the hobby enthusiast. This backyard oasis is sure to impress!  Hurry- this home will not last long at this price point!
